Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Strong Unit Mix with 5 x 2 Bed Units

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present 1 Abbott Street, Coogee to market. 

The property offers incoming investors with a secure income stream, supported by the comfort of residential real estate in Sydney's Eastern Suburbs. 

Property highlights include:
- Strong unit mix comprising of 5 x 2 bedroom apartments
- All apartments have balconies and allocated off-street parking 
- The building sits elevated on the Northern side of Coogee boarding Clovelly  
- North-easterly aspect provides strong sun into all apartments 
- Located in walking distance to Randwick Shopping Village, Coogee Beach & Shops 
- All amenity provides public transport to Sydney's CBD 

This property is located on a quite a tranquil street, away from any main roads yet provides easy access to various transport options and notable locations like Coogee Beach, Coogee Pavilion and Coogee Bay Hotel.

1 Abbott Street, Coogee will be sold via Public Auction on Tuesday 9th of March 2021 at 10:30am at AuctionWORKS (live stream & online bidding available).

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*approximates

Note: All financial figures have been provided by the
Vendor. Purchasers are advised to conduct their own
independent due diligence.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BOUTIQUE APARTMENT BLOCK IN SYDNEY'S EASTERN SUBURBS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and First National are pleased to present to market 346 Arden Street, Coogee. Situated in a premium location, 346 Arden Street, Coogee is a two storey building comprising a total of 4 x 2 bedroom apartments. All of the apartments are well proportioned and provide prospective purchasers with a secure residential investment with a steady cash flow in a highly sought after Eastern Suburbs neighbourhood. The property also presents the ability to further capitalise through value-adding or strata subdividing. The close proximity to beaches, dining and retail amenities provides a desirable opportunity for individuals or
families that wish to be a part of the ‘laidback Australian beach lifestyle’ within Sydney’s highly desirable Eastern suburbs region.

346 Arden Street, Coogee benefits from the following key attributes:
- Deceased Estate
- Existing improvements of 4 x 2 bedroom apartments
- Significant land area of 632sqm*
- R2 Low Density zoning (permitting dwelling/ semi-detached dwellings/ dual-occupancies)
- 9.5m height limit
- Premium location centrally located close to Coogee Beach,
retail strip and bus services
- North-East facing aspect on elevated hillside

*Approximate

346 Arden Street, Coogee will be sold via an On-Site Auction on Saturday, 24 July 2021 at 9:00am.

Inspections to be held by appointment as per COVID-19 Greater Sydney restriction requirements. Please enquire directly with the exclusive agents to arrange a private viewing. 

To assist in the assessment of this offering, due diligence can be obtained from the exclusive selling agents.

CBRE, as the exclusive selling agent, is pleased to present 173-177 Coogee Bay Road, Coogee. Exclusively positioned within walking distance to Coogee Beach, the property is a mixed use apartment block containing eight units and two ground floor retail suites fronting Coogee Bay Road. 173-177 Coogee Bay Road benefits from the following key attributes:
•	8 residential apartments comprising a mix of:
- 2x1 bedroom apartments
- 5x2 bedroom apartments
- 1x3 bedroom apartment
•	2 tenanted ground floor retail suites
•	Gross income of $308,969 per annum*
•	NLA 632.4sqm*
•	Land area 490sqm*
•	High-profile location in Coogee’s beachside retail precinct
•	Opportunity to strata subdivide and sell down individually in strong performing local property market
•	Located in a suburb well positioned to benefit from the incoming Randwick Light Rail
•	350m* from Coogee Beach and 1km* from future Randwick Light Rail Interchange

The property will be offered for sale via public auction on Tuesday, 27 March 2018 at 10.30am at AuctionWORKS.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BEACH SIDE MIXED USE APARTMENT BLOCK

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive sales agents are pleased to present to you, 162 Arden Street, Coogee. 

162 Arden Street, Coogee is currently a vacant single storey house with DA approval for a luxury residential apartment block. The DA consists of a 4 storey block comprising 6 x 1 bedroom apartments and a 1 x 2 bedroom penthouse. The scheme has been architecturally designed focusing on utilising the space while offering superior orientation providing significant exposure to natural light and ocean views.

The property benefits from being perfectly located in a quiet yet sought after location and only metres from Coogee Beach, retail and other amenities. 

162 Arden Street benefits from the following key attributes: 


- DA approved for 7 luxury apartments with ocean views
- Highly sought-after location
- Land area: 405sqm*
- Proposed NSA: 366sqm*
- Walking distance to Coogee Beach, dining and retail amenities
- Zoning: R4 High Density Residential with 12 metre height limit
- Direct transport to Sydney CBD

162 Arden Street, Coogee will be offered for sale via public auction on Tuesday 15th October 2019 at 10.30am at AuctionWORKS, 50 Margaret Street, Sydney. 

For more information, please contact the exclusive sales agents.
